products.title: Enjoy Dimout Frosted White Roller Blind
products.description: Plain white roller blinds are so last year. Its time for something more contemporary, something more innovative. Like this enjoy dimout frosted white roller blind. One piece of fabric, rolled to create a double layer, with alternating dimout and open weave strips throughout.
